snippet.title: Polyphony Trailer
snippet.description:
Polyphony is a short hack designed to provide a challenge to players of all skill levels! Whether a player who's never played kaizo venturing down the primary route, or a seasoned veteran exploring the far reaches of the Polyphonic Isles, there's something for everyone in this hybrid kaizo/standard hack!

Music: Cyan Beast - Homestuck
